title: Norm And Abnormal Norman - Born Again T.V. Music Videos
description:
Norm And Abnormal Norman was formed in 2014 by Lige Williamson and Kyle Stersic in Boulder CO, but have since then relocated to Brooklyn NY. They play and compose in a variety of styles centered around blues, jazz, country, folk, singer-songwriter, and avant-garde
 
Lige Williamson - Slide Guitar, Accoustic Guitar, Electric Guitar, Mandolin, Harmonica, Lead Vocals;

Kyle Stersic - Alto/Tenor Saxophone, Whistles, Piano, Organ, EWI, Barbie Guitar, Circuit Bent Shit, Cassette Sampling/Looping, Vox

"Norm And Abnormal Norman And The...." music videos shot by Merritt Crocker. On our Youtube channel, it has links to all the other NAAN music videos. If you like this music, check out this music.
